{"tid":57483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨退休被揭監守自盜偷八達通　資深警判監21日","createTime":"2016-12-28T05:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T01:29:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35b7ae875156c19bdfaa3083b871026de5fba278","tid":57483,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"當差36年、原定還有不足一個月便退休的資深警察，今年初在被扣押車輛內偷竊2張八達通卡並取得八達通退款，他早前承認2項盜竊罪，裁判官今日取得其背景報告，判其監禁21日，扣減被還押的日子後可即時釋放。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，54歲被告何膺然在九龍灣車輛扣留及檢驗中心當值期間，因管有扣押車輛車匙，在2輛汽車內偷取2張八達通卡，再向港鐵申請注銷，獲退款約150元。後來物主在取回涉事車輛時，發現車內八達通不翼而飛，最終警方翻查閉路電視片段後鎖定被告。<br />\n<br />\n被告今日在觀塘裁判法院候判，他求情指，21日的監房生活令他感受到自由的寶貴，他深深地感到後悔，希望裁判官從輕發落。裁判官取得其背景報告後，判處被告監禁21日，扣除他被還押的日子後，可當庭釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161228/s00001/1482898603291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161228%2Fs00001%2F1482898603291&d=MP5r6eUwNfSjSFn0NXIBn2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c8168d49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161228%2Fs00001%2F1482898603291&h=0af8fd4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161228/s00001/1482898603291</a>"},{"pid":"f119b63e0cc6afc272efa1f8091aa57b8e8fcac9","tid":57483,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"仲有無長糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490c51caef83d120be19478534ac1732f8e21b3f","tid":57483,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有無長糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刑事仲要坐應該乜都無晒"},{"pid":"cab19e83ec3fa130d6329a33f36a0682d6940399","tid":57483,"uid":46842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"差佬<img src=\"/asse